					    <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane animateIn" id="collection-information">
					    	<h2 class="primary-title text-primary-color animateIn">Collection of Information</h2>
					    	<p>In the normal course of operating our Sites and providing our Services, we may collect, store and process personal information that you make available to us when accessing or using our Services. This personally identifiable information may include a User’s name, e-mail address, street or mailing address and mobile phone number (“Personal Information”). In particular, Personal Information may include:</p>
					    	<ul class="comman-list list-inside">
